query:
WITH
    to_update AS (
        SELECT
            UNNEST($1::TEXT[]) cs,
            UNNEST($2::DATE[]) date
    )
UPDATE fuel_estimates f
SET
    status = $3
FROM
    (
        SELECT
            w.fiskeridir_vessel_id,
            to_update.date
        FROM
            to_update
            INNER JOIN fiskeridir_ais_vessel_mapping_whitelist w ON w.call_sign = to_update.cs
    ) q
WHERE
    q.fiskeridir_vessel_id = f.fiskeridir_vessel_id
    AND f.date >= q.date
